--- ip ---
ip | ip6 address | range

  Display informations about the IP address or range in argument.

examples:
---------

  lsfw> ip 1.2.3.4/21
  ip      : 1.2.3.4
  network : 1.2.0.0 - 1.2.7.255
  netmask : 255.255.248.0
  prefix  : 21
  length  : 2048

  lsfw> ip 1.2.3.4 - 1.2.3.255
  range  : 1.2.3.4-1.2.3.255
  length : 251
  nearest network : 1.2.3.0 - 1.2.3.255
  netmask : 255.255.255.0
  prefix : 24
  network length : 256

  lsfw> ip6 afnic.fr
  ip      : 2001:660:3003:2:0:0:4:20
  network : 2001:660:3003:2:0:0:4:20 - 2001:660:3003:2:0:0:4:20
  prefix  : 128
  length  : 1
